# ⭐ Step 3：轉長表（FIFO 必備）

```sql id="q9m2yx"
SELECT
    月份,
    col,
    val
INTO #Base
FROM #Raw
UNPIVOT (
    val FOR col IN (_0002, _0011, _0020)
) u;
```

---

# ⭐ Step 4：拆需求 / 供給

```sql id="8d2mnc"
SELECT *
INTO #Demand
FROM #Base
WHERE val > 0;

SELECT 
    月份,
    col,
    -val AS supply
INTO #Supply
FROM #Base
WHERE val < 0;
```

