# ⚠️ 三、重點（FIFO核心）

SQL 沒有 Python while loop，所以 FIFO 通常有兩種做法：

---

# ⭐ 方法 A（簡單版）：累積法（推薦）

👉 適合 80% business scenario

```sql id="p3v8kt"
SELECT
    d.月份 AS demand_month,
    s.月份 AS supply_month,
    d.col,
    CASE 
        WHEN d.val <= s.supply THEN d.val
        ELSE s.supply
    END AS alloc
FROM #Demand d
JOIN #Supply s
  ON d.col = s.col;
```

👉 但這個是「粗配對」，不是完全 FIFO 消耗

---

# ⭐ 方法 B（完整 FIFO）：Recursive CTE（你 Python 對應版）

```sql id="r8k2lp"
WITH match_cte AS (
    SELECT
        d.月份 AS demand_month,
        s.月份 AS supply_month,
        d.col,
        CASE 
            WHEN d.val <= s.supply THEN d.val
            ELSE s.supply
        END AS alloc,
        d.val AS remaining_d,
        s.supply AS remaining_s
    FROM #Demand d
    JOIN #Supply s
      ON d.col = s.col

    UNION ALL

    SELECT
        demand_month,
        supply_month,
        col,
        CASE 
            WHEN remaining_d > remaining_s THEN remaining_s
            ELSE remaining_d
        END,
        CASE 
            WHEN remaining_d > remaining_s THEN remaining_d - remaining_s
            ELSE 0
        END,
        CASE 
            WHEN remaining_s > remaining_d THEN remaining_s - remaining_d
            ELSE 0
        END
    FROM match_cte
    WHERE remaining_d > 0 AND remaining_s > 0
)
SELECT *
FROM match_cte;
```

